        <Meaning id="40916d12-db93-4279-be92-9852b0c6bd14" type="Verb">
          <Vi>mua</Vi>
          <En>To obtain something by paying money for it.</En>
          <Example>I decided to buy a new laptop after comparing prices online.</Example>
          <IsArchaic>false</IsArchaic>
          <Situations>
            <Situation id="e0701e53-1810-4351-9c16-e0398cd32baa">
              <Vi>Mua hàng hóa hoặc dịch vụ từ cửa hàng, người bán, hoặc nền tảng trực tuyến.</Vi>
              <En>Purchasing goods or services from a store, seller, or online platform.</En>
            </Situation>
            <Situation id="a0b00f89-771c-4504-8a36-31a395f0bd72">
              <Vi>Dùng trong các cụm từ như “buy time” (mua thời gian), “buy into an idea” (tin tưởng, chấp nhận một ý tưởng).</Vi>
              <En>Used in idioms such as “buy time” (to delay action) or “buy into an idea” (to accept or believe in an idea).</En>
            </Situation>
          </Situations>
